---
    title: Basement
---
{% extends "boilerplate/landing_base.njk" %}



{% block content %}
<section class="section hero narrowSection1_5 invertColor">
    <h1>Ottawa’s Basement Renovation & Finishing Experts</h1>

    <div class="container">
        <div class="container">
            <p>Looking to transform your unfinished or outdated basement? Hughes Home Services provides trusted basement renovations, remodels, and finishing services across Ottawa. Whether you're adding a family room, home office, or rental suite, we’ll turn your vision into a clean, livable space—done right, on budget, and with zero hassle.</p>
            <img src="/assets/IMG_132.jpg" alt="" class="mainImg">
        </div>
        <div class="container spread">
            <span class="ratings">
                <img src="/assets/review_stars.svg" alt="" class="stars">
                <span>Rated 5/5 Star Service</span>
            </span>
            <h2 class="h2-promo1">Serving Nepean, Kanata, and the Greater Ottawa Area</h2>
            <ul class="-spr-list-1">
                <li class="p-promoBig">Basement Finishing & Remodels</li>
                <li class="p-promoBig">Full Basement Renovations</li>
                <li class="p-promoBig">Bathroom, Kitchen & Flooring Upgrades</li>
                <li class="p-promoBig">Custom Layouts, Soundproofing & More</li>
            </ul>
            <a class="-b-spec-3Big" href="tel:6134221991">Call Today</a>
        </div>
    </div>
    <div class="bg"></div>
</section>

<section class="section bgContrast1 invertColor narrowSection1_5">
    <ul class="-l-4Col_card-1">
        <li class="-card-spec-card3">
            <img src="/assets/stats_experience.svg" alt="" class="icon">
            <h3>30+</h3>
            <p class="-t-pSmall">Years of Experience</p>
        </li>
        <li class="-card-spec-card3">
            <img src="/assets/stats_customers.svg" alt="" class="icon">
            <h3>20+</h3>
            <p class="-t-pSmall">Years of Loyal Customers</p>
        </li>
        <li class="-card-spec-card3">
            <img src="/assets/stats_projects.svg" alt="" class="icon">
            <h3>100+</h3>
            <p class="-t-pSmall">Annual Projects</p>
        </li>
        <li class="-card-spec-card3">
            <img src="/assets/stats_homedepot.svg" alt="" class="icon">
            <h3>Home Depot</h3>
            <p class="-t-pSmall">Part of the Pros Team At Home Depot</p>
        </li>
    </ul>
</section>

<section class="section -l-2Col-offerForm narrowSection1_5">
    <div class="offerContainer">
        <img src="/assets/promo1/offer_quote.png" alt="">
    </div>
    <div class="formContainer dropshadow1 spread">
        <h2>Get a Free Basement Renovation Quote</h2>
        <form class="-form-1" name="contact" netlify>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input required type="text" name="name" id="name">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input required type="email" name="email" id="email">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                <input required type="tel" name="phone" id="phone">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea required name="message" id="message" placeholder="Tell us about your basement project..."></textarea>
            </div>
            <input class="-b-spec-3" type="submit" value="Send Message">
        </form>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section -l-about bgContrast1 invertColor narrowSection1_5">
    <div class="imagesContainer">
        <img src="/assets/IMG_6623.jpg" alt="" class="mainImg">
        <img src="/assets/IMG_6765.jpg" alt="" class="mainImg">
    </div>
    <div class="">
        <h2 class="h2-promo1">A little About Wendall And Hughes Home Services</h2>
        <br>
        <p>Hughes Home Services was founded by Wendall Hughes, who started working in his family’s general contracting business at a young age. With over 30 years of experience in Ottawa, Wendall leads a team focused on honest, skilled work and personalized service for every home project.</p>
        <br><br><br>
        <h2 class="h2-promo1">Part of the Home Depot's Pros Team</h2>
        <br>
        <p>We’re proud to be part of Home Depot’s trusted Pros Team—recognized for our consistent quality, reliability, and professionalism in Ottawa’s home improvement industry.</p>
        <br><br><br>
        <h2 class="h2-promo1">Why Ottawa Calls Us First for Basement Projects</h2>
        <br>
        <p>Our team specializes in basement finishing and remodeling projects that add value and functionality to homes. Whether it’s a home theatre, guest suite, or a quiet office, we handle the details other companies overlook—with clean work, efficient timelines, and clear communication every step of the way.</p>
    </div>
</section>

<section class="section -l-2coloverlap_container_image-left-1 bgHalfContrast1 invertColor narrowSection1_5">
    <div class="container spread bgContrast1 invertColor">
        <h2><div class="-t-smallHighlight">Contact</div>Partner with Ottawa’s Trusted Basement Renovation Pros</h2>
        <form class="-form-1" name="contact" netlify>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="name">Name</label>
                <input required type="text" name="name" id="name">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="email">Email</label>
                <input required type="email" name="email" id="email">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="phone">Phone Number</label>
                <input required type="tel" name="phone" id="phone">
            </div>
            <div class="inputContainer -inputContainer-1">
                <label for="message">Message</label>
                <textarea required name="message" id="message" placeholder="What would you like to do with your basement?"></textarea>
            </div>
            <input class="-b-spec-3" type="submit" value="Send Message">
        </form>
        <div class="imgWrapper"><img src="/assets/IMG_6764.jpg" alt=""></div>
    </div>
</section>

{% endblock %}